## Erlkoenig ELF Analysis Service
## No epmd — custom erlkoenig_epmd module resolves ports.
## -erl_epmd_port tells relx which port to use for erl_call.
## Distribution port pinning + interface binding is in sys.config.

-name erlkoenig_elf@127.0.0.1
-setcookie ${RELX_COOKIE}
-start_epmd false
-epmd_module erlkoenig_epmd
-erl_epmd_port 9103

## Scheduler wakeup: respond quickly to socket requests
+sbwt very_short
